{"tid":1416373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香城系統再咨詢》入黎理性地表達下意見","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:08:59.000Z","uid":263218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0e355780f86d7182683e942b1b4a2ee970d2f4","tid":1416373,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"修訂咨詢建議如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果增設左膠苦行憎<br />\n<br />\n2. 修訂火魔法師攻擊對象<br />\n<br />\n3. 系統維護一星期<br />\n<br />\n4. 為612基金、立場、獨媒、義士團體課金<br />\n<br />\n5. 成立民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n6. 連登政治討論日<br />\n<br />\n7.  香城上線100天/ 120天 / 150天紀念行動（機場）<br />\n<br />\n8. 增設 證據審查師 / 法律研究員 <br />\n<br />\n9. 宣傳口號更新，免遭系統誤判<br />\n<br />\n10. 囤購物資、更新裝備 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e50e8f2fcb8daf12ec0879d353330efc5efe0e","tid":1416373,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7de4554123eaba765c9d6593f4d12ae78936e1","tid":1416373,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93020944cffaa3be2b9248d5ecdcccba05108181","tid":1416373,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e507b6aaa0545538f063ce1a38065050e9e3ff2f","tid":1416373,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"11. 營辦反送中消費合作社"}]}